subject: Tennis
French Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Justine Henin-Hardenne won the French Open, picking up her third title on the clay at Roland Garros and capturing her fifth Grand Slam championship over all, by defeating Svetlana Kuznetsova, 6-4, 6-4.
